{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.760", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.000", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es immer wieder interessant, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man Parallelen zwischen der FDP und der Linkspartei feststellen kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens geht es dabei um die Flucht vor der Verantwortung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.840", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie beide wollen nicht regieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.360", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie beide ziehen es vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.360", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aus der Ecke des Plenarsaals zu krakeelen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.120", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen von der FDP, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.120", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Senkung des Beitragssatzes zur Arbeitslosenversicherung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.280", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die R\u00fccklage gef\u00fcllt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "h\u00e4tten wir vereinbaren k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir hatten auch schon eine Zielsetzung im Hinblick auf die Gesamtsozialversicherungsbeitr\u00e4ge vereinbart. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.560", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All das h\u00e4tten Sie haben k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.040", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie nicht Angst bekommen h\u00e4tten und vor der Verantwortung geflohen w\u00e4ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von der Linken kennen wir es ja schon seit vielen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vielen Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.440", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie die Verantwortung scheuen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.440", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich muss an dieser Stelle sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.520", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer vor den Souver\u00e4n tritt und sagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.680", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eIch m\u00f6chte eine Stimme f\u00fcr mein politisches Angebot\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.360", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der muss auch in schwieriger Lage den Stier bei den H\u00f6rnern packen und Verantwortung \u00fcbernehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.760", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr sind wir hier."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.520", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der zweite Punkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.760", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an dem es Parallelen zwischen Ihnen gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.000", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die geradezu groteske \u00dcberzeichnung des Sozialstaats, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.800", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nat\u00fcrlich in unterschiedlicher Richtung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.720", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie von der FDP sehen den Sozialstaat bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.800", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sozialversicherungen ausschlie\u00dflich als Kostg\u00e4nger der Wirtschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.360", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als Kostenbelastung und nicht als Einrichtungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.160", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Chancen f\u00fcr die Menschen und damit die Voraussetzungen f\u00fcr Freiheit schaffen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo wird dies deutlicher als bei der Arbeitslosenversicherung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei der wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerade angesichts der Digitalisierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.960", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weiterentwicklungsbedarfe haben? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.880", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf gehe ich gleich noch ein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.840", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Linken gibt es eine groteske \u00dcberzeichnung und Vereinseitigung des Sozialstaatsbegriffs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.840", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da Sie den Sozialstaat vorwiegend als gigantische Alimentationsmaschine verstehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.640", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Debatte um die von Ihnen geforderte Mindestsicherung in H\u00f6he von 1\u00a0500\u00a0Euro"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0nach Berichtigung des Druckfehlers sollen es jetzt nur noch 1\u00a0050\u00a0Euro sein\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.880", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist in gewisser Weise sehr erhellend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.920", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man wundert sich \u00fcber Ihre Forderung nach 1\u00a0500\u00a0Euro n\u00e4mlich gar nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mich auch nicht wundern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie da die Zahl\u00a02 \u00a0000 hingeschrieben h\u00e4tten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind von Ihnen n\u00e4mlich gewohnt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bei den Zahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie in Ihre Antr\u00e4ge schreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.240", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Skala nach oben offen ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.040", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wirft ein bezeichnendes Licht auf Ihre \u00dcberzeichnung des Sozialstaatsbegriffs."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.640", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt m\u00f6chte ich auf die Aufgabe der Arbeitslosenversicherung eingehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.160", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.400", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bevor wir \u00fcber die Kosten reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.040", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Aufgabenkritik vornehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcsste eigentlich l\u00e4nger ausfallen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.880", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als mir an Redezeit noch zur Verf\u00fcgung steht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.920", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte das Beispiel der Digitalisierung aufgreifen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.320", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Digitalisierung ist n\u00e4mlich verbunden mit der immer schnelleren Entwertung des Wissens von Besch\u00e4ftigten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.000", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ausbildungsinhalte ver\u00e4ndern sich immer schneller. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.160", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es besteht ein kontinuierlicher Weiterbildungsbedarf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.360", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wem beim Thema Digitalisierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.080", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Theurer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.280", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nichts anderes einf\u00e4llt als eine Steuer- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.760", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Beitragssatzsenkung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.120", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der hat den Prozess mit seinen ganzen tiefgreifenden Umbr\u00fcchen \u00fcberhaupt nicht verstanden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.560", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir brauchen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.240", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in diesem Punkt muss die Arbeitslosenversicherung weiterentwickelt werden\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.600", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist zum Beispiel ein Anspruch auf Weiterbildung schon w\u00e4hrend der Besch\u00e4ftigung und nicht erst wenn der Fall der Arbeitslosigkeit eingetreten ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade bei \u00e4lteren Besch\u00e4ftigten in kleinen Betrieben besteht ein enormer Nachholbedarf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.600", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insgesamt ist der Umfang der betrieblichen Weiterbildung Gott sei Dank angestiegen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.720", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber gerade dort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.560", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo einfache T\u00e4tigkeiten durch die Digitalisierung in Zukunft ersetzt zu werden drohen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.400", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "manchmal ist es auch gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass monotone T\u00e4tigkeiten ersetzt werden\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.200", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir einen Bedarf an pr\u00e4ventiver Weiterbildung und haben Vorsorge zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.000", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Arbeitslosenversicherung in diesem Sinne fit zu machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.840", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00fcrde zu einer umfassenden ganzheitlichen Betrachtung geh\u00f6ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.800", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr stehen wir als B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen und werden daf\u00fcr k\u00e4mpfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.920", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das h\u00e4tten wir auch gerne in einer Regierung getan."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.680", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.960", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat Dr.\u00a0Albert Weiler f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}